1. He has expressed a desire to change or be different.
2. His current behavior or state is not in line with his true intentions.
3. He has conflicting feelings or desires.
4. His actions are not aligned with his stated goals or preferences.
5. He may be feeling pressured or coerced into being a certain way.
6. He is in the process of self-reflection or change.
7. His true self is not the same as the way he appears or presents himself.
8. He is not being true to himself or his authentic nature.